metadata.name: Can't Be Stopped - Ethereum Collection [1/20]
metadata.description:
This digital collectible is edition 1/20 of the Genesis Salt Season - Ethereum Collection. It is matched with a unique item of clothing which can be redeemed against this digital collectible only once.

The Genesis Salt Season consists of two unique collections and each edition of the Ethereum Collection has a Bitcoin counterpart. It's creation marks the birth of the Salt & Satoshi brand.

It is the first of a series of collectibles made by SaltDAO - a decentralized autonomous organization working to develop new and novel ways for people to create, collect and experience items and merchandise.
